txt.en: 'So, you want to get to Seregost? I suppose I can help with that.'\n\nCompleting this quest will unlock access to the Bloody Watchers in Agarnaith and the Seregost level 115 area.
'Off you go! Say hi to Viznak for me!'
Completion of this quest will allow you access to the Seregost endgame area for testing.
